\title{Andrew Czezowski}
\taxon{Person}

\p{Aspiring physics student. I recieved my BSc Honours Physics-Chemistry from the [University of Manitoba](https://www.umanitoba.ca/) in 2024. I've worked 2 km underground with the [PICO Collaboration](https://www.picoexperiment.com/) at [SNOLAB](https://www.snolab.ca/). My research interests are in particle theory, currently focusing in dark matter candidates and in fundamental interactions.}